{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.960", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr verehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.800", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Staatsministerin Gr\u00fctters! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.520", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.200", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wesen der Kunst ist es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.800", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neues zu schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.720", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Altes gegen den Strich zu b\u00fcrsten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.480", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu \u00fcberraschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schillernd, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.640", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "h\u00e4sslich oder auch konfrontativ zu sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kunst muss uns nicht gefallen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.200", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nicht an uns als Politiker, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.680", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kunst zu beurteilen oder sie gar durch Vorgaben einer sogenannten Leitkultur zu g\u00e4ngeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.360", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die \u00c4lteren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich m\u00f6chte nicht sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.960", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ganz Alten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.520", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen sich vielleicht an die letzte\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Anf\u00fchrungszeichen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.000", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201ekonservative Revolution\u201c erinnern,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.080", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Mitte der 1980er-Jahre von CDU und CSU unter Kanzler Kohl in der Bundesrepublik als geistig-moralische Wende ausgerufen wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Recht viel mehr als das Privatfernsehen und die Schwarzgeldkonten hat sie f\u00fcr unser Land nicht gebracht,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.680", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sehr viel mehr ist auch vom Begriff der Leitkultur nicht zu erwarten,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.240", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der inhaltlich bis heute wie \u201eeine Flasche leer\u201c ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.560", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.640", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kulturpolitik muss die Voraussetzungen schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit Kunst entstehen kann\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.920", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in all ihrer Vielschichtigkeit als Ausdruck unserer freien Gesellschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.000", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade heute, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.600", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da wir uns mit der Spaltung unserer Gesellschaft konfrontiert sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.360", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss ein entscheidendes Ziel die kulturelle Teilhabe f\u00fcr alle sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.760", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei muss auch der Kulturbetrieb raus aus der Wohlf\u00fchl\u00adecke und diese Aufgabe mit Lust und Freude annehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.880", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Koalitionsvertrag geht von einem offenen Kulturbegriff aus; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das begr\u00fc\u00dfe ich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.480", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie erkennen die Notwendigkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.800", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die soziale Lage von Kreativen zu verbessern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allerdings soll der Bericht dazu erst im Laufe der Legislaturperiode kommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum so sp\u00e4t?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.360", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das erschlie\u00dft sich nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie schon in Ihrem Koalitionsvertrag von 2013 k\u00fcndigen Sie eine sachgerechte Anschlussregelung beim Arbeitslosengeld an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie diese Regelung ausgestaltet werden soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.400", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bleibt nach wie vor offen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem jetzigen Koalitionsvertrag wecken Sie viele Erwartungen bei den Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.440", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Kulturbetrieb t\u00e4tig sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie gehen damit eine gro\u00dfe Verpflichtung ein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.080", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Opposition werden Sie kontinuierlich daran erinnern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.800", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Vertrag mehr sein muss als sch\u00f6ne Worte auf Papier;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.360", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.880", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Kulturbetrieb t\u00e4tig sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.680", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "brauchen ganz konkrete Verbesserungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was sie brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.000", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die soziale Absicherung von Kreativen und Selbstst\u00e4ndigen mit geringem Einkommen durch die Einbeziehung in die sozialen Sicherungssysteme."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen hier mehr als Pr\u00fcfabsichten der Regierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen sozial-, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "arbeits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.680", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und vertragsrechtliche Mindeststandards, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerade dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Kreative nicht fest angestellt sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.800", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das alles brauchen wir schnell."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.240", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kulturf\u00f6rderung muss transparenter und gerechter werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.120", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frauen sind in den Entscheidungsgremien des Kulturbetriebs noch immer deutlich unterrepr\u00e4sentiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.080", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Kulturf\u00f6rderung muss die verbindliche geschlechtergerechte Quote gelten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.160", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.520", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie kennen das Schiller-Wort von der Kunst als \u201eTochter der Freiheit\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.040", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass K\u00fcnstlerinnen und K\u00fcnstler sowie Kreative sich einmischen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.560", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.280", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie uns andere Sichtweisen er\u00f6ffnen und uns mit ihren Talenten bereichern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir als Deutsche uns als Kulturnation verstehen und r\u00fchmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.200", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann m\u00fcssen wir uns heute f\u00fcr die Freiheit der Kunst und gegen jeden Versuch der Normierung und G\u00e4ngelung einsetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.640", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.200", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir kommen zum Themenbereich Digitalisierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich erteile das Wort der Staatsministerin Dorothee B\u00e4r."
   ]
  }
 ]
}